CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

March 30, 2005

[Cite as 03/30/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1303.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2004-1874. State ex rel. Cincinnati Bell Tel. Co. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss. On S.CtPrae.R. X(5) determination, cause dismissed as moot. See State ex rel. Cincinnati Bell Tel. Co. v. Pub. Util. Comm., 105 Ohio St.3d 177, 2005-Ohio-1150, 824 N.E.2d 68.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
